Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来叫您起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 早上就这么吵 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:02:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂是不会为你做这些事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做不做 我也不想让她这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用害羞 对我许愿的话 不管什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不纯洁！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小孩子是否太过刺激了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩这样的玩具的话 永远都不能为别人去实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远都当不了大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有人来打搅 接下来的等会再做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以的 我也能实现别人的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是去大学吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又干了些什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是说过了吗 没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在履行1级神应尽的义务而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为2级神的你是无法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了 身为1级神的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没时间像你一样整天无所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 赢给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩欧丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:25.54,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFF6C6C&}{\3c&H00D5D5&}啊啊 想帮上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看谁才是更能帮助人的女神 来一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单的游戏 不是契约
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是玩真的 又会违反规定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一做评委 没什么好抱怨的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也没办法 就来一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂你们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出你的愿望来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一很为难的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是担心我把他抢走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来参加这场胜负怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能的话 萤一的愿望也早就实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我差不多要去大学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回来再慢慢说好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的瞬间移动法术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这把传送枪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间飞行术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不亏是一级神的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都要被我的法术所眩目了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的机器是世界第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决战的舞台转到大学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你追去也没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法实现他愿望的你追去了也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帮助萤一 其实只能让他更困扰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本 从那个时候起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对你那伪善者的样子很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩欧丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样一个自我陶醉下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能实现萤一的愿望的人不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会将这一点证明给你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个已经被田宫前辈他们弄坏过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个铜象虽然已经用木工用粘合剂粘上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是吃不消一个人的体重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经为时已晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节 掉进水里果然够爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买点热的饮料来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛衣 come here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强力塑料膜涂层火箭筒 SET
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季节变化程式 Summer Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛衣被…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我做的还是很完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说2级神的手法还是太天真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到底会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不想也知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 蓓儿丹蒂还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因为什么奇怪的事而烦恼就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么做才能让你感到安心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 这个还是很热的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有蓓儿丹蒂在身边 我竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然还是喜欢那种东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不纯洁 但我还是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下所期待的果然还是女性身体的神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让你看个够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 我变成风了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化为风是男人的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题吧 到底发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风系的法术不是我的专长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要使用不擅长的法术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕我们的法术互相混淆后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没让风刮起来 而是把萤一变成了风本身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一会和风完全的融合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再恢复原来的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是换来的是可以尽情一览裙下的风光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩欧丝 法术的取消呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个被扭曲了的公式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道能不能解开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以萤一 到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个巨大的风团中把萤一找了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是擅长风系法术也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个乱来的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难以致信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂把那个混乱的公式解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于只知道蓓儿丹蒂天上界的一面的你\N来说的确很难理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之坦白的承认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了 输了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂 我们回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 姐姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 姐姐他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没能说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是给你添麻烦 而我什么都没能为你做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 萤一只要想着我 我就很高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白 到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是那样的萤一 蓓儿丹蒂才会如此地信赖他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要让萤一的心里只有我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个异常甜蜜的氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 真的对这样小学生的家家酒就满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 绝对没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才已经确认过了你对异性的需求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下 即使强硬手段我也要让他就范
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大化药Giant－X
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中呼吸药P－1－0
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子 全是些无聊的药
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键的药到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这药只会服用者变得见一个爱一个 真没品味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来华丽地改良它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命名之－爱情甘露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让他只会喜欢上我的高雅之药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扫～打扫～真快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}打扫～打扫～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩欧丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完成了萤一的愿望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样身为一级神的我真为你感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作为一个女神到现在究竟做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能为人们实现一切愿望的才是一级神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是我们的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在逃避这个义务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义务…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借口就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想实现他心中的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那些而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天也有流汗的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是怀疑我在杯子里放了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直是用这样的眼光来看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我喝就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是没放什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到刚才为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒来的时候你的眼中将会只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是萤一吗 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一正在休息中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是去那边不要在这里打搅他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 佩欧丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想实现萤一全部的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作为一级神的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是从心底里想这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点晚了 我来看你们的照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了 哎 在这里睡着会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小惠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢…喜欢…好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.39,0:16:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了是兄妹间的亲情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现到了小萤作为一个男人的{\fn经典粗黑简}魅力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不要再做兄妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是做兄妹吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么回应我这份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会回应呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萤 开门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吵死了 都听不到电视的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张抽筋一样的脸和这一直不变的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满野性实在美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先冷静下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萤 最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 差不多药效也该出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 打开你的心扉把你的愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小萤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么都请说出来吧 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数了几次还是少了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来帮帮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德吗 帮帮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 把脸转过去下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩欧丝好象让你吃了爱的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的种子 记得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像把爱的种子进行了加工
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它变成了能让服用者变得人见人爱的诱惑剂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要作出那样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的药剂 半吊子的水平是用不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做解毒剂 你等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 如果连蓓儿丹蒂也变成这个样子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是后来的 真是厚脸皮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抢我的小萤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱可没什么规则
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这么说的话 那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看我 佩欧丝做的\N爱的种子肯定会让你也变怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我面对面真的那么痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样我也想留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想留在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我还不能实现佩欧丝所说的那种萤一的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的想实现萤一所有的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是身为一级神的义务 而是我自己想为你来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样的我 萤一也能接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起的话 也许会遇到更痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你在一起感到痛苦的事一次都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只要你能陪伴在我的身边 我的愿望就实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这光芒 是多么的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象做了个噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我也中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我突然想起来有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 但是在这之前有件事想请教你下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:20:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去过你的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿走了你的药以及想独占萤一的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事情我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是一级神 不能说谎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么首先就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我都不知道要怎么办才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我要说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这事 蓓儿丹蒂又不得不去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么药对蓓儿丹蒂不起作用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是当然的
